 Project Title: Smart Expense Analyzer
 Description

This project analyzes a user's monthly expenses using Python operators and determines their financial status. It demonstrates how basic operators can be applied to real-world financial calculations.

 Concepts Covered
Arithmetic Operators (+, -, *)
Comparison Operators (>, <)
Logical Operators (and)
Assignment Operators (+=)
Conditional Statements (if, elif, else)
 Features
Calculates total monthly expenses
Determines savings based on salary
Compares different expense categories
Evaluates financial condition (Good, Average, Low Saving)
Updates salary with a 10% bonus
Key Learnings
Applying Python operators in real-life scenarios
Writing clean and structured conditional logic
Performing financial calculations programmatically
Understanding how multiple conditions work together
